Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,'Cuz I wanna keep laughing!\NMOVIN'! MOVIN'!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.36,0:23:55.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in charge of Bount\Ncountermeasures?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.77,0:23:56.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.83,0:23:58.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lirin. A Mod Soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.67,0:24:00.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,An expert at tracking Bounts!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.67,0:24:02.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Is that true?\N– Unfortunately it's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:04.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you want, I'll lend her to Squad 10.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll pass.\NI have a bad feeling about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.02,0:24:08.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How insulting!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.38,0:24:19.39,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers\NGolden after these messages!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.39,0:24:22.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N– Golden!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.24,0:24:24.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro! What happened to that kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:28.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Renji! He's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.19,0:24:29.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's out of danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.67,0:24:32.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Thank goodness…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.69,0:24:35.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:36.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In Soul Society!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.64,0:24:38.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are kind, Renji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.83,0:24:41.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You came all this way\Nto check on him…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.20,0:24:43.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's one thing, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.56,0:24:47.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I was told\Nto clean up before I leave…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.39,0:24:49.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– What?!\N– Quickly…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.35,0:24:57.36,OS,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose--!